data.description: Under contract-accepting backup offers. Location, Location!! This beautiful 3/2 with den and pool home is located in the heart of Town and Country. Near shops, restaurants, schools, grocery stores, Mall and the beach. Open concept, perfect for entertaining and  a bonus room that can be use as an office or other bedroom. Bay window in master bedroom that provides plenty of natural light and with the right sofa a perfect reading or relaxing area. Plenty of natural light through the house, high ceilings and a cute screened outdoor space with a pool, ideal for those hot summer days and nice to enjoy during those cooler days, another great area for entertaining with friends and family. Your next home is waiting for you!   Investors, this property is already generating rental income.
